*"Results are what matter. Side effects are data."*

**Operator:** Eirin Yagokoro

Superior healing supplies and — for those willing to accept some uncertainty — experimental alternatives at reduced cost. Eirin explains everything once. She does not repeat herself.

**Standard Inventory:**
| Item | Effect | Price |
|---|---|---|
| Healing Potion | 2d4+2 HP | 50gp |
| Greater Healing Potion | 4d4+4 HP | 150gp |
| Superior Healing Potion | 8d4+8 HP | 400gp |




| Supreme Healing Potion | 10d4+20 HP | 1,000gp |
| Antitoxin | Advantage on saves vs. poison for 1 hour | 50gp |

**Dubious Experiments** *(healing potion cost reduced by 50%)*:

Roll **d10** when consuming:
| d10 | Effect |
|---|---|
| 1 | Heal normally — no side effect |
| 2 | Heal for maximum HP value |
| 3 | Heal + Dramatic Wind — clothing and hair flutter heroically for 1 hour |
| 4 | Heal + Language Shift — lose Common, speak a random known language for 1 hour |
| 5 | Heal + Rhyming Compulsion — can only speak in rhymes; non-rhyming speech is unintelligible for 1 hour |
| 6 | Heal + Voice of Echoes — voice echoes dramatically as if in a grand cathedral for 1 hour |
| 7 | Heal + Poison Immunity — immune to poison damage and poisoned condition for 1 hour |
| 8 | Heal + Uncontrollable Hiccups — breaks concentration and stealth for 1 hour |
| 9 | Heal + Glowing Skin — emits soft magical light (5ft bright radius; visible while invisible) for 1 hour |
| 10 | Heal + Squeaky Voice — voice becomes absurdly high-pitched for 1 hour |

**Notes:**
- Eirin will not explain what "dubious" means in advance. That would defeat the purpose.
- She accepts material components from the tower as partial payment (DM discretion)
- Reisen assists when present; Eirin handles the unusual cases herself
